(20, 'Counterflow Cooler', 'کولر ضد جریان', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Yemmak counterflow cooler is used for cooling the feed that is\r\nout from pellet mill in pellet form which is hot, to ambient temperature. It\r\nworks according to steady air form principle. Air in the external environment\r\ncontacts the feed in the cooler; while the temperature of the feed drops, warm\r\nair is removed from the environment through air aspiration system.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Discharge system which is on the cooler, removes cooled feed.\r\nDrainage system can be chosen with grid or hydraulic valve depending on the\r\npreferred product. Drainage system is adjustable and works according to the\r\ncapacity.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\">کولر ضد جریان</span><span dir=\"LTR\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">کولر Counterflow یماک برای خنک کردن خوراک داغی که به صورت پلت شده از دستگاه آسیاب پلت خارج&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">می گردد&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">استفاده می شود</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;که خوراک را به دمای محیط برساند.</span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">این کار با توجه به اصل فرم پایداری هوا کار می کند.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">هوا در محیط خارجی تماس غذا را در کولر برقرار می کند؛</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">در حالی که دمای خوراک کاهش می یابد، هوای گرم از طریق سیستم آسپیراسیون هوا از محیط خارج می شود</span></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\"><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span dir=\"LTR\"></span>.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">The temperature is controlled with the levels on the body. The\r\nfeed dust in the warm air that moves to the aspiration system, are sent back to\r\nthe system with the cyclone. After cooling, pellet feed durability. This way,\r\ndust output while packaging is prevented. Also, it gets optimum humidity and\r\nthis way, pellet quality is extended. There are single or dual deck models\r\navailable for intended use.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Myriad Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.3333px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">FEATURES</span></b></div></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Easy\r\n     assembly with modular body<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Efficient\r\n     cooling wih the airlock located in the product entry<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Homogenous\r\n     product distribution system<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Mesh\r\n     modelled, motorized or hydraulic drive for discharging system<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Level\r\n     indicator<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Temperature\r\n     indicator<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n</ul>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\">سیستم تخلیه ای که بر روی کولر قرار دارد، غذای\r\nخنک را حذف می کند.&nbsp; سیستم زهکشی را می\r\nتوان با توجه به محصول ترجیح داده شده با شیر شبکه یا شیر آب انتخاب کرد.&nbsp; سیستم زهکشی قابل تنظیم و با توجه به ظرفیت کار\r\nمی کند،سطح دما توسط یک کنترل کننده که روی بدنه دستگاه قرار دارد تنظیم می شود</span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\">.&nbsp; گرد و غبار\r\nخوراک موجود در هوای گرم که به سمت سیستم آسپیراسیون حرکت می کند، با جریان باد به سیستم برگردانده میشود.پس از خنک شدن، دوام پودر\r\nخوراک افزایش می یابد،به این ترتیب،از تولید گرد و غبار در\r\nهنگام بسته بندی جلوگیری می شود.&nbsp; همچنین،\r\nرطوبت مطلوب از این طریق به دست می آید و به این ترتیب، کیفیت پلت افزایش می یابد.مدل های عرشه تک یا دوگانه برای استفاده در نظر\r\nگرفته شده است که هردو مدل موجود می باشد.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span dir=\"LTR\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span dir=\"LTR\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\">امکانات</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\"></span></p><ul><li style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\">شاخص دما</span></li><li style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\">شاخص سطح</span></li><li style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\">مونتاژ آسان با بدنه ماژولار</span></li><li style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\">سیستم توزیع محصول همگن</span><span dir=\"LTR\"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\">سیستم مدل مش، موتور با سیستم هیدرولیک برای\r\nتخلیه سیستم</span></li><li style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\">خنک کننده کارآمد همراه با ورودی هوا در دهانه ای ورود محصول است</span></li></ul>', '1510523413pelet-sogutucu-en-3.pdf', NULL, 14, '1510523413Counterflow-Cooler-1.jpg'),
(21, 'Fine Grading Hammer Mill', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: &quot;Myriad Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Micronized mills are convenient for grinding fish feed, pet food\r\nand other materials which need to be fine-grained, in large capacity\r\nproduction. Micronized mills’ grinding tanks are in 650mm diameter, have 1200\r\nmm width to 1000 mm lenght. Operation speed is 3000/3600 RPM. Mills with\r\nfine-graining equipment can provide high quality feed in large capacities,\r\nwhile protecting the nutritional value of the feed with their low operating\r\ntemperatures.<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-right:7.5pt;text-align:right;\r\ndirection:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">آسیاب های میکرونیزه برای خوراک ماهی و مواد غذایی حیوانات خانگی و سایر موارد گه نیاز به ریزه کاری و تولید در ظرفیت بالا دارند مناسب است.مخازن سنگ زنی آسیاب میکرونیزه دارای قطر 650 میلی متر و عرض 1000 تا 1200 میلی متر می باشند.سرعت عملیات 3000/3600 دور در دقیقه است،</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">میلز با تجهیزات\r\nریز دانه می تواند <a href=\"http://www.novinniroo.co\" target=\"_blank\">خوراک با کیفیت بالا</a> را در ظرفیت های بالا فراهم کند، در حالیکه\r\nارزش غذایی تغذیه را با دمای پایین آن حفظ می کند.</span></span><span dir=\"LTR\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Magnetic seperator in the tank assures that foreign materials\r\nwon’t pose a fire hazard or harm the tank itself. It provides the maximum\r\noperating safety.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">The material to be grained is sent to the mill by twin feeder\r\nscrews. To assure the operational safety, the twin feeder screws send the\r\nmaterial in correspondence to the electrical engines’ power consumption.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Myriad Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.3333px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">FEATURES</span></b></div></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Wide\r\n     capacity ranges<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Low\r\n     investment, operational and maintanence costs<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Maximum\r\n     flexibility and variety<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Quality\r\n     assured Grade A performance<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; c