(24, 'Micro Dosing', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Weighing system consists of a steel construction. It has a\r\npowder absorption feature for eliminating dust coming out of the silos.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Myriad Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 11.5pt;\">The screws that are used for dosing have a diameter of 100mm.\r\nThere is a pneumatic slide on the output to prevent the products from spilling.\r\nIt has a flexible design with the dosage scales. The sensitive weighing system\r\nin the dosage scales transports the weighed product to the mixer with the help\r\nof the pneumatic butterfly valves.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Myriad Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.3333px;\"><br></span></font></div>\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]-->\r\n<!--[endif]--><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Myriad Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">سیستم توزین از ساخت و ساز فولادی تشکیل شده است.&nbsp; این ویژگی جذب پودر برای حذف گرد و غبار خارج از سیلو ها است.</span><br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#333333\">FEATURES</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Weighing\r\n     sensitivity<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Flexible\r\n     formula combination<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">A\r\n     fully automated controlled process<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Flexible\r\n     system<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Myriad Pro&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Dustless\r\n     design<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;پیچ هایی که برای دوز استفاده می شوند دارای قطر 100 میلی متر هستند.&nbsp; اسلاید پنوماتیک بر روی خروجی برای جلوگیری از ریختن محصولات است.&nbsp; این طراحی انعطاف پذیر با مقادیر دوز دارد.&nbsp; سیستم توزین حساس در مقیاس دوز محصولات با وزن را به میکسر با کمک شیرهای پروانه ای پنوماتیک حمل می کند.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><br></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;امکانات</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\">&nbsp;• حساسیت وزن</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\">&nbsp;• ترکیب فرمول انعطاف پذیر</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\">&nbsp;• یک فرایند کنترل کاملا خودکار</span><br><span style=\"font-siz